---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Programmes | Brenkley Doctoral College" description="All Brenkley Doctoral College doctoral programmes — DBA, EdD, Online PhD, Extended Advanced Diploma, Access to Doctorate, Research Training, and Supervisor Development.">

  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Study with Brenkley Doctoral College</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Programmes</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Brenkley Doctoral College offers a range of doctoral and professional development programmes designed for working professionals. Whether you are ready for a full doctorate or exploring the pathway, we have a programme for you.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Doctoral Programmes -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Doctoral Degrees</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Professional Doctorates &amp; PhD</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-6">

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Doctor of Business Administration (DBA)</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">The Brenkley Doctoral College DBA is designed for senior business and management professionals who want to conduct rigorous original research within their professional context. Over three years part-time, you develop as a researcher, deepen your theoretical understanding, and produce a thesis of genuine significance.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
                <span><strong>Duration:</strong> 3 years part-time</span>
                <span><strong>Delivery:</strong> Online + residential</span>
                <span><strong>Fee:</strong> £8,500/year</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/programmes/dba" class="btn-primary flex-shrink-0">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Doctor of Education (EdD)</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">The EdD is designed for education professionals — teachers, school leaders, further education practitioners, education policy professionals, and university academics — who wish to conduct doctoral-level research into educational practice, leadership, or policy.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
                <span><strong>Duration:</strong> 3 years part-time</span>
                <span><strong>Delivery:</strong> Online + residential</span>
                <span><strong>Fee:</strong> £7,500/year</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/programmes/edd" class="btn-primary flex-shrink-0">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Online PhD</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">Brenkley Doctoral College's fully online PhD offers maximum schedule flexibility for researchers who cannot commit to a fixed residential schedule. Study is entirely online, with a duration of three to six years depending on pace. Suitable for researchers in any professional context, nationally or internationally.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
                <span><strong>Duration:</strong> 3–6 years part-time</span>
                <span><strong>Delivery:</strong> Fully online</span>
                <span><strong>Fee:</strong> £6,500/year</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/programmes/online-phd" class="btn-primary flex-shrink-0">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Extended Advanced Diploma — Year 1 of the PhD</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Research Degree</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">The Extended Advanced Diploma is a standalone research degree and Year 1 of the Brenkley Doctoral College PhD. Over eighteen to twenty-four months, you conduct supervised original research, submit a substantial thesis, and complete an applied internship putting your findings into practice. Credit-rated at SCQF Level 11, 180 credits, with the option to progress to Years 2–3 at a partner university of your choice.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
                <span><strong>Duration:</strong> 18–24 months part-time</span>
                <span><strong>Delivery:</strong> Online + optional residential</span>
                <span><strong>Fee:</strong> £4,800/year</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/programmes/mphil" class="btn-primary flex-shrink-0">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pathways and CPD -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Pathways &amp; CPD</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Preparation &amp; Professional Development</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Access to Doctorate</h3>
            <span class="tag tag-training">Pathway</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">A one-year preparation programme for professionals considering doctoral study but not yet ready to apply directly. Covers research thinking, academic writing, and research design fundamentals.</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted mb-4"><strong>Fee:</strong> £2,800 total</div>
          <a href="/programmes/access-to-doctorate" class="btn-outline text-sm">Learn more</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Research Training</h3>
            <span class="tag tag-training">CPD</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Modular research methods training available as standalone CPD or integrated within a doctoral programme. Modules include Research Design, Qualitative Methods, Quantitative Methods, and Academic Writing.</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted mb-4"><strong>Fee:</strong> £1,500 per module</div>
          <a href="/programmes/research-training" class="btn-outline text-sm">Learn more</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Supervisor Development</h3>
            <span class="tag tag-training">CPD</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">A professional development programme for doctoral supervisors. Covers supervisory practice, ethical responsibilities, supporting doctoral wellbeing, and contemporary challenges in doctoral education.</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted mb-4"><strong>Fee:</strong> £1,200 total</div>
          <a href="/programmes/supervisor-development" class="btn-outline text-sm">Learn more</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Help choosing -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Not sure which programme is right for you?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">Book a free, no-obligation conversation with our admissions team. We will help you understand which programme fits your background, research interests, and professional goals.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/connect" class="btn-primary">Book a conversation</a>
        <a href="/apply" class="btn-outline">How to apply</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
